This is Perl module Watch4.

INSTALLATION

Watch4 installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up,
you should just be able to do

% cpan Watch4

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

% perl Makefile.PL
% make && make test

Then install it:

% make install

DOCUMENTATION

Watch4 documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

% perldoc Watch4
